name: gpflow
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.1.1" %}

package:
  name: gpflow
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: GPflow-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/GPflow/GPflow/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e92737e9488360aca754c24da434118c625aa9737bc22d2a58e41caf7c3f9122

build:
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python >=3.5
    - pip

  run:
    - python >=3.5
    - numpy >=1.10.0
    - scipy >=0.18.0
    - pandas >=0.18.1
    - tensorflow
    - multipledispatch >=0.4.9
    - pytest >=3.5.0

test:
  imports:
    # Skip the import test on Linux, see tensorflow recipe
    - gpflow  # [not linux]

about:
  home: https://github.com/GPflow/GPflow/
  license: Apache 2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Gaussian process methods in tensorflow

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cxhernandez
    - jschueller
